actions.name: Randomize
actions.handler: (chart) => { const options = chart.getOption(); let base = +new Date(1968, 9, 3); let oneDay = 24 * 3600 * 1000; let date = []; let data = [Math.random() * 300]; for (let i = 1; i < 20000; i++) { var now = new Date((base += oneDay)); date.push([now.getFullYear(), now.getMonth() + 1, now.getDate()].join('/')); data.push(Math.round((Math.random() - 0.5) * 20 + data[i - 1])); } options.series.forEach((series) => { series.data = data; }); chart.setOption(options); }
